1
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,280
Senior Master!

2
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:17,519
Senior Master!

3
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:43,000
Senior Master!

4
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:26,680
Senior Master!

5
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:31,120
I haven't even performed the discipleship ceremony for you.

6
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:38,919
You are supremely righteous.

7
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:45,520
Senior Master did all this for us.

8
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:49,560
If we continue to waste time here,

9
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,919
we'd truly be letting him down.

10
00:03:54,719 --> 00:03:55,840
Staff Officer He is right.

11
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:57,560
For Senior Master,

12
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,159
we must find the Lingxiao Pearl even if we die.

13
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,680
Senior Master!

14
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,319
Teacher Lu.

15
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,120
Old Lu, stop crying.

16
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,159
Let's go.

17
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:21,720
These trees are different from naturally growing plants.

18
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:23,600
Someone planted them in specific positions

19
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,680
on purpose.

20
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,399
The positions of these trees

21
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:39,959
coincide with the Twenty-Eight Lunar Mansions.

22
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:41,920
When the Dian King was alive,

23
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,360
he indeed compared himself to the Ziwei Star.

24
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:44,399
But to become an immortal,

25
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:45,639
he would definitely place himself

26
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:46,600
in the place closest to heaven

27
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,560
to guard the heavenly gate.

28
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:50,120
I know.

29
00:05:50,399 --> 00:05:51,680
Corresponding to the star map,

30
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,160
it should be the head of the Seven Mansions of the East,

31
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,519
Jiao Xiu.

32
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,120
Let's go.

33
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,079
It's getting hotter as we walk.

34
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,480
I can't take it anymore.

35
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,720
I'm dying of heat.

36
00:06:28,879 --> 00:06:30,160
Why am I getting hotter

37
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:31,560
and hungrier as I walk?

38
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:34,199
How about we rest here for a bit?

39
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:36,519
We can peel some bark and boil it to eat.

40
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,560
What is this?

41
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,800
What is it?

42
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,600
It's snowing.

43
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:50,959
No way.

44
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,920
How can it snow in Southern Yunnan?

45
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,639
On such a hot day,

46
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,560
it would probably just fall as steam.

47
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,519
Exactly.

48
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:03,160
This looks like volcanic ash.

49
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,600
Are there volcanoes in Southern Yunnan?

50
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,560
Of course there are.

51
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,120
There's an active volcano nearby.

52
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,920
Chen Youxi, what are you thinking?

53
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,519
Do you guys remember

54
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:15,120
when we looked down from the Heavenly Gate earlier?

55
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,680
This rainforest looks like a giant crater.

56
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:27,839
Bro,

57
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:32,360
are we inside a volcanic crater?

58
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,120
We've said many times before

59
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:36,600
that crustal movements occurred in Guyu.

60
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,920
So, being in a volcano...

61
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,680
That's not surprising at all.

62
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:41,879
Along our way here,

63
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,480
the temperature has indeed been rising.

64
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,720
And there were earthquakes too.

65
00:07:45,279 --> 00:07:47,199
Now it seems to be the movement of underground magma.

66
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:48,560
Stop talking about this.

67
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,519
Let's think about that old Dian King.

68
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,879
You could say he had a big head but low IQ.

69
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:55,199
Putting his tomb in a volcanic crater,

70
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,920
wasn't he afraid of burning his own butt?

71
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,560
Crustal movements are inherently unpredictable.

72
00:07:58,879 --> 00:07:59,879
The Dian King's Tomb being built here

73
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:00,759
only proves that

74
00:08:00,759 --> 00:08:02,399
after the Dian King's Tomb was completed,

75
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:04,319
the volcano never erupted.

76
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:07,720
Why did we have to be so unlucky to run into it?

77
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:11,680
Aren't we just choosing to beard the lion

78
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:13,000
in his den?

79
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:14,199
Let's go. Let's go back.

80
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:15,240
Let's go. Let's go back.

81
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,040
Let's go back, Old Lu.

82
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,160
We're almost at that tree ahead.

83
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:20,199
Right now, it's just the temperature rising.

84
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,279
The volcano won't erupt anytime soon.

85
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,800
We need to find the Lingxiao Pearl before that happens.

86
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,839
Exactly. We aren't that unlucky.

87
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:26,360
Let's go.

88
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,759
Hurry up, everyone. Let's go.

89
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,639
What is this thing?

90
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:55,120
Look at this.

91
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,080
And this stone tablet.

92
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,799
And that giant statue. Isn't it...

93
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,399
Isn't it the same as the one

94
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,360
we saw in the tomb passage murals?

95
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,919
Sister Shutong said this is an altar.

96
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,120
Isn't it the same?

97
00:09:06,279 --> 00:09:07,639
This is a good thing.

98
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:10,120
We've pretty much explored all of Guyu.

99
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,759
We've been everywhere we should go.

100
00:09:12,159 --> 00:09:13,559
All that's left is the Dian King's Tomb.

101
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:17,679
Bro, victory is right ahead.

102
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,960
Let's hurry up and get moving.

103
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,840
Let's go, let's go.

104
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:34,279
Wait.

105
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:43,000
If we really are in a volcanic crater...

106
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:45,840
Then...

107
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,000
What are you trying to say?

108
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,159
It's too dangerous ahead.

109
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:58,399
Should we... Should we...

110
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:04,759
Shutong! Shutong!

111
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:10,320
Shutong!

112
00:10:13,879 --> 00:10:14,559
Shutong!

113
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,320
Shutong, what exactly are you doing?

114
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,320
Can't you see what I'm doing?

115
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:23,360
Can you calm down and let me finish?

116
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:25,440
No. I know what you want to say.

117
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,600
The volcano is definitely going to erupt.

118
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,399
I can't let all of you lose your lives.

119
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,440
Along this journey,

120
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:35,519
haven't we almost lost our lives many times?

121
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,360
Haven't we made it through together?

122
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,799
This time is different from before.

123
00:10:38,799 --> 00:10:40,759
Before, whether it was traps or human threats,

124
00:10:40,759 --> 00:10:41,759
we could solve them.

125
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:44,960
Let me ask you, if the volcano erupts,

126
00:10:45,399 --> 00:10:46,399
who can escape?

127
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:52,600
We finally found the Dian King's Tomb.

128
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,399
We can't just pack up and go home now.

129
00:10:57,559 --> 00:11:00,080
Old Chen! Old Chen, come look!

130
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:19,799
This should be

131
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:22,759
the tree we're looking for, right?

132
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:11,200
This tree even produces milk. It's oozing.

133
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,000
Is it salty or sweet?

134
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,720
Don't move!

135
00:12:16,879 --> 00:12:17,320
What's wrong?

136
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:19,320
This is called the Blood-sealing Tree.

137
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:20,960
The white sap is highly toxic.

138
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,320
If processed well, it can be used as medicine.

139
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:25,720
If not, it kills instantly upon contact with a wound.

140
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,279
That's right.

141
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:29,320
Poison Arrow Tree.

142
00:12:32,639 --> 00:12:33,320
But...

143
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:36,799
If the Dian King's Tomb is really in this tree hole,

144
00:12:36,799 --> 00:12:38,440
this hole is full of deadly poison.

145
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,440
How do we get in?

146
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,679
As long as there are no wounds,

147
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:41,840
it won't affect us.

148
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:42,919
Wounds...

149
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,919
We've arrived.

150
00:12:48,799 --> 00:12:49,799
Do we go in or not?

151
00:12:51,279 --> 00:12:52,080
You decide.

152
00:12:52,279 --> 00:12:53,919
What do you mean, go in or not?

153
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,559
We absolutely have to go in.

154
00:12:56,159 --> 00:12:57,879
Old Chen, don't forget

155
00:12:58,240 --> 00:13:00,600
what Senior Master said before he died.

156
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:03,360
We owe him a mountain of gratitude.

157
00:13:03,919 --> 00:13:05,200
No matter what you guys think,

158
00:13:05,519 --> 00:13:07,120
even if it costs me my life,

159
00:13:07,559 --> 00:13:09,720
I must see that Lingxiao Pearl for him.

160
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,039
Me too.

161
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:51,200
Old Chen, can we go down?

162
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:54,200
It's safe. Come on in.

163
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:25,639
There's always a world beyond ours.

164
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,279
I didn't expect this.

165
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:29,360
Inside such a huge banyan tree,

166
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,159
there's actually a cave like this.

167
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,639
These things that look like stalagmites

168
00:14:33,639 --> 00:14:36,159
must be tree sap solidified over the years.

169
00:14:38,519 --> 00:14:39,120
What's wrong?

170
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,559
Why is it dripping so much liquid?

171
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,399
The tree sap is melting.

172
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:47,200
It must be due to the rising temperature.

173
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,720
Very likely.

174
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:51,200
The underground magma activity raises the surface temperature,

175
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,720
causing the tree sap to melt.

176
00:14:58,799 --> 00:15:00,000
It really is melting.

177
00:15:00,519 --> 00:15:03,120
I-If it gets any hotter,

178
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:05,279
it'll all melt and we'll be soaking in it.

179
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:07,000
Once it dries, won't we become amber?

180
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:07,919
T-This won't do.

181
00:15:07,919 --> 00:15:08,679
Let's go, let's go.

182
00:15:08,679 --> 00:15:09,440
Go where?

183
00:15:09,519 --> 00:15:11,120
Bro, come take a look.

184
00:15:17,559 --> 00:15:18,720
There seems to be something inside.

185
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:19,960
Let's take it out.

186
00:15:20,799 --> 00:15:21,960
The Dian King's treasure box

187
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:24,120
is completely encased in this tree sap.

188
00:15:24,159 --> 00:15:25,120
There's no other way.

189
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,679
We can only wait for the sap to melt.

190
00:15:26,799 --> 00:15:27,879
Wait? Wait until when?

191
00:15:29,559 --> 00:15:29,879
It's fine.

192
00:15:29,879 --> 00:15:32,120
Isn't the underground temperature rising right now?

193
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,039
Yeah.

194
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:35,320
Our torches are just the icing on the cake.

195
00:15:35,519 --> 00:15:37,120
The temperature here keeps rising,

196
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,559
so the outer shell of this treasure box

197
00:15:38,559 --> 00:15:40,120
shouldn't take too long to melt.

198
00:15:40,919 --> 00:15:43,360
Just now we were saying how unlucky we are

199
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:45,120
to run into a volcanic eruption.

200
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,360
N-Now...

201
00:15:47,399 --> 00:15:48,200
Right, right, right.

202
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:50,320
This is called a fortunate twist.

203
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:54,279
Fortune and misfortune are intertwined.

204
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:55,000
Intertwined, intertwined...

205
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,120
S-Stop intertwining already.

206
00:15:57,720 --> 00:15:58,399
Look.

207
00:15:58,840 --> 00:15:59,519
It melted.

208
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,720
So this is the Lingxiao Pearl.

209
00:16:38,279 --> 00:16:39,120
There's no mistaking it.

210
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:40,960
Compared to the one in Yunling,

211
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,200
although the color is slightly different,

212
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:44,480
it has the same aura.

213
00:16:45,879 --> 00:16:46,960
Aren't you afraid of getting sick?

214
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:47,919
Touching it with your bare hands.

215
00:16:49,399 --> 00:16:50,120
Let me do it.

216
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,200
I'm the only one who isn't afraid of getting sick.
